FT  26 AUG 94 / Observer: French leave
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The dismissal of Chung Myung-whun as music director of Paris's Opera
Bastille is causing a furore back in his home country of South Korea. His
compatriots regard the sacking as an insult to their national honour, even
though Chung is now a US citizen.
