FT  25 AUG 94 / UK Company News: Net assets slip to 227.24p at Jos
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Jos Holdings, a split capital investment trust, reported a net asset value
per capital share of 227.24p at the July 31 year end, against 277.9p six
months earlier and 217.29p at end-July 1993.
